Space imports are failing with the following error message displayed on the UI:
{noformat}Import failed. Check your server logs for more information. com.atlassian.confluence.importexport.ImportExportException: Unable to complete import: Error while importing backup: org.hibernate.exception.ConstraintViolationException: could not execute statement{noformat}

h3. Environment
* Confluence Cloud 1000.518.1

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Perform a space import

